{"tid":949002,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"{皇天擊殺}   一人一個傳銷狗典型開場白/技倆","createTime":"2018-12-20T13:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T14:52:15.000Z","uid":9338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07d35d913f7dc526588b789304bb73e559e859fc","tid":949002,"uid":9338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟咁啱之前中過招，<br />\n俾個熟人昆咗去傳銷，<br />\n本來佢話咩可以齊齊做生意<br />\n<br />\n話自己間野跨國又盛，乜嘢彈性工作時間，<br />\n唔駛辛苦有錢袋乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n又講到唔駛讀書都可以喺嗰度成功咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好，我初頭俾條友氹我落疊，水咗小小錢<br />\n<br />\n後來越諗越唔對路<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦點會有咁便宜嘅事，<br />\n跟住返屋企一睇，屌你老味，間垃圾原來個死人朵已經臭曬<br />\n<br />\n跟住返到去第二日，冇再入過間垃圾，順便屌柒條仆街之後再同條友劃清界線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知我蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你自己利用呢種關係去賺呢挺不義之財，你遲早會俾天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你依家睇緊呢個post, <br />\n我想同你講：<br />\n你條撚頭咪咁得戚，若然未報，時辰未到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多行不義必自斃，你自己做咩你自己知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac501b34972a8a41221c797a2f970d9fd1790fe","tid":949002,"uid":9338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f742a0be83cdb7031e5fc53726f3793869febf","tid":949002,"uid":26522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"蠢你就蠢啦，俾人水到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6189c6134eac5fe51e9c56402515b63cd711cf1","t